This paper deals with data poisoning attacks in the context of online learning, which is a problem that is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. However, given that the paper proposes a control approach that uses deep reinforcement learning, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, since the paper deals with security and attacks, it could also be classified under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
